      "position": { "x": -720, "y": -280 },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "title": "Bridge Export Surface Smoke Test",
        "subtitle": "Verify that one bridge can expose a class export or a kit export intentionally, and that the legend only reflects the declared export surface.",
        "intent": "headline",
        "status": "active",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "title",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/template-structure/title.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/template-structure/title.node-class.node"
        },
        "_bridge": {
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/template-structure/title.node-class.node",
          "kind": "node-class",
          "targetKind": "node-class",
          "classKey": "title",
          "classRef": "/library/classes/nodes/template-structure/title.node-class.node"
        },
        "definitionKey": "title"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-export-smoke-instructions",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Instructions",
      "position": { "x": -720, "y": 80 },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Procedure\n\n1. Select each bridge and turn on `Create` in the node face or Properties panel.\n2. Leave the surface blank unless you are intentionally testing a different surface.\n3. Open the legend.\n4. Confirm that the legend gains only the exported vocabulary for that bridge.\n5. Create at least one node from each bridge-backed export.\n\n## What This Tests\n\n- `github-repo` should behave as a **class export**.\n- the task template should behave as a **kit export**.\n- the document template should behave as a **kit export**.\n- presence in the target graph is not enough; only the declared export surface should count."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-export-smoke-expected",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Expected Results",
      "position": { "x": -120, "y": 80 },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Expected Results\n\n### GitHub Repo Class Export\n- legend should expose `github-repo`\n- it should not expose unrelated classes from the class graph\n\n### Task Template Kit Export\n- legend should expose planning vocabulary such as `goal`, `task`, `open-question`, `decision`, `summary`, and `script`\n- it should not expose every node merely because it exists in the template\n\n### Document Template Kit Export\n- legend should expose document vocabulary such as `title`, `section`, `document-summary`, `document-view`, `reference`, `figure`, `embed`, and `annotation`\n- it should not expose unrelated template internals\n\nIf any bridge resolves but yields no legend entries after `Create` is on, capture the bridge JSON and diagnostics."
      }
    },
